com.interpss.core.aclf.hvdc
Interface ThyConverter

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Subinterfaces:
Inverter, Rectifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
InverterImpl, RectifierImpl, ThyConverterImpl
public interface ThyConverter
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Thy Converter'.

The following features are supported:

  • Firing Ang
  • Firing Ang Limit
  • NBridges
  • Ac Rated Voltage
  • Commuting Z
  • Xformer Ratio
  • Xformer Tap Setting
  • Xformer Tap Step Size
  • Xformer Tap Limit
  • Commuting Capacitor

See Also:
HvdcLinePackage.getThyConverter()
